# ThreatForge Output — SIGNATURES
# CVE:       CVE-2026-55005
# Product:   microsoft exchange
# Tags:      [HIGH] [T1]
# Score:     40
# Tier:      STANDARD
# Generated: 2026-07-21T04:31:48.442758Z
# Status:    OK
